{"tid":1381104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線勇武手足, 我想盡量提高「由前線決定」既效率","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:58:12.000Z","uid":33763,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bcb816fefbdd143008d154ff43b0a351239ea7","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"TLDR: 睇underline左既字<br />\n<br />\n事緣我睇到依個post<br />\n[前線心態調整] 我係勇武，我覺得衝，都要目標導向，Objective-Oriented<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378355</a><br />\n<br />\n依幾日見到前線有手足守住大街, 但最尾被班畜生捉左好多<br />\n好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完依個post, 我係到諗<br />\n前線既巴絲,不如按照你地既想法, <ins>由你地黎定當日目標</ins><br />\n好似71咁, 前線手足想衝立法會既, 同我地一班和理非/文宣講聲<br />\n<ins>我地會幫你正名, 話俾其他人知前線做緊咩, 同埋帶動其他人支持你地</ins><br />\n就算你地既目標係引班狗出醜都唔緊要<br />\n一眾手足會無條件支持你地既決定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我都見有好多人話勇武「磨爛蓆」<br />\n實際上可能係佢地已經有目標, 但太多人唔知所以先咁講<br />\n但我希望<ins>前線有目標既話, 講聲俾我地知, 等我地幫你</ins><br />\n<ins>目標達成之後, 如果冇即時既目標, 我地就散</ins><br />\n唔想再有咁多人被狗捉<br />\n我地係一體, 有你地依場運動先可以走落去<br />\n絕對支持你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n不割蓆, 不篤灰<br />\n不撤．不散"},{"pid":"f7e0e41290e48354108d9463ee2b11d4cd2774ac","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"試下十連"},{"pid":"60c8d3858b6bc408b3d6808c8832d23e30c7d849","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5b4b3a8bd0643cbf98c3c39939f19b90ad69af1","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dba817a1b40267507c0d39aa734e20c56f3cf15a","tid":1381104,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d2da540ab3565c5473f61c84471af6149ad0ecb3","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2fc679a305ad657c612a7b166f761a690c9b6bd","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"十連失敗都推"},{"pid":"87dd8beccc1489b2152248675efbc6fdd84b3158","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b77831521fbe41163834634ad64998fc848be128","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbfb9954341ab8cd24c19ab2633e6e85f80f886a","tid":1381104,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9890a83825a55d8e56ea17a77fc6f8ce80ecc481","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:18:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a89bd96357f4c26f7afc4a3c4966006a532da726","tid":1381104,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n溝通重要"},{"pid":"30fde7ecd4ede7eadb8ee77e3829c97ff62681e4","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"唔止前線決定去留<br />\n更由佢地決定當日運動既目標<br />\n再由我地幫手達成佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6061b6879071f871385a2fa424cce8d5a00fa19c","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"一路睇班狗up官腔一路推"},{"pid":"de0c29a7080f964c7d4d372182307d110480c5ed","tid":1381104,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"其實就咁前線都好難溝通<br />\n<br />\n就咁最前線嗰排打橫咁都溝通唔到，成日一邊退，隔離嗰邊又唔跟住退"},{"pid":"cf1d775fe59167ae2361ea7fcc4fab957c255dda","tid":1381104,"uid":24814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e03482f6e770dac9166ec2f1635818b2cd172d2","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de0c29a7080f964c7d4d372182307d110480c5ed","tid":1381104,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"其實就咁前線都好難溝通<br />\n<br />\n就咁最前線嗰排打橫咁都溝通唔到，成日一邊退，隔離嗰邊又唔跟住退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"我都明<br />\n但除左我地依啲明白前線既人之外<br />\n仲有好多人(例如班街坊)唔知佢地想做啲咩<br />\n依樣野都係盡力做"},{"pid":"14caeccbb23ccd3d4091af10c486f7cbfe239c3f","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1d775fe59167ae2361ea7fcc4fab957c255dda","tid":1381104,"uid":24814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"辛苦一班前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔會膠到叫前線做小組討論決定去留<br />\n只係希望前線有可能的話<br />\n溝通一下, 決定當日目標<br />\n最好就交換埋TG, 確保冇鬼<br />\n決定到既話就搵巴打所講既通訊兵通知其他人<br />\n包括網上睇直播既朋友"},{"pid":"262914d300ffc1e28a76cd94c1f2a3bf009f588b","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"推到前線手足睇到"},{"pid":"c6975bc96e1fc9747bc9fcecf15daaa3a86c87c4","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0303f9ebc996cd87ec98964f1283eeee5aa345b0","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed0b7e7da034a76cf713256819aa12ddb1396778","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2082e4d7009b29e1f94c2d5fc1eca5fcbfb8f6b6","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a89f2aac3adecad02089f6574c6a6b3ce581f2b0","tid":1381104,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5efb322604feaf6d25233bc4f7a5e4db13eb844b","tid":1381104,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a6457b2f151eea75ca43bf336fc4e13972a552cc","tid":1381104,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57a2fd389b487b235a83b5d827c926767872c58d","tid":1381104,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:38:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"091d2082b7712382ffd327caee43ae69a45e3017","tid":1381104,"uid":285536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"我地連罷工、老豆接仔放工都未試<br />\n香港人 唔好放棄!<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n*7月30 : 地鐵不合作運動 <br />\n*8月2 : 公務員罷工集會<br />\n*8月5 : 一齊罷工 7區集會 <br />\n返工放工幫手air drop<br />\n停止前線義士受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n我要真普選 不要空降假特首"},{"pid":"f26926acbf5fcb6dc25e6be6604866a6b1260375","tid":1381104,"uid":33763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 時代革命"},{"pid":"e7b0a3948715df3f2ad52d65df69ce30bbd62f18",